description: The Cookie Cabin is cruising through Louisville and serving the fine people of the streets a delightful selection of warm cookies, ice cream, and of course...ice cream sandwiches. Your sweet tooth is sure to love every bite of these fresh-baked batches; there’s Chocolate Chunk, Oatmeal Raisin, Snickerdoodle, and White Chocolate Macadamia too! And with delicious ice cream in between, it’s no wonder everyone is going wild for the treats from The Cookie Cabin!
name: The Cookie Cabin
